                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": It maps the overpunch character in the last position of the string to its corresponding numeric value and sign. This involves a predefined mapping where specific characters represent digits 0-9 with either a positive or negative sign."
